            "title": "梁文鋒量化基金去年回報達57% 為DeepSeek提供堅實資金後盾",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"梁文鋒量化基金去年回報達57% 為DeepSeek提供堅實資金後盾\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"745\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ctFw7s6wrWvSUwPeTr0vHQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc0NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-01/3a813af0-df20-11ef-bfad-dd3d361b41fc\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">梁文鋒量化基金去年回報達57% 為DeepSeek提供堅實資金後盾</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
