        {
            "title": "台灣利率市場：公債交易冷清 IRS橫向盤整；短票利率略走軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國12月份非農就業報告好壞參半，國債殖利率曲線隔夜出現「扭曲式走平」，周一亞洲盤因日本休市而未開盤；台灣方面，電子盤未見成交，各年期IRS橫向盤整。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">元大證券於報告中指出，指標5年券的標售結果沖淡市場原先偏空的氣氛，月底前尚有350億的兩年券待標售，加上在強勁的經濟數據支持以及股市創高的情況下，台灣央行今年尚看不到降息的機會，預料投資盤雖有補券需求但在次級市場對利率也會較為堅持</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預估本周5年券成交區間在1.28%-1.33%，10年券成交區間在1.38%-1.43%</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貨幣市場</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a1bd069d-e7f4-318e-80d7-01e4db8298df-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據票券商與銀行人士稱，市場資金稍微分布不均，不過不影響整體調度狀況，短票利率甚至有朝低檔回落的態勢，拆款利率則是大致持平；部分銀行因盤點農曆新年換新鈔所需資金，態度較為保守。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據兩位銀行資金調度人士稱，同業間資金狀況偏寬鬆，但也有部分資金水位較平，對交易採取觀望態度</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其中一位拆出一周資金給小銀行，利率維持在1.40%</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據兩位票券商人士表示，上門推銷資金的銀行仍不少，僅有少數態度較為保守，短票利率區間低檔略有回落，拆款利率大致持平</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與銀行承作30天期的自保短票利率成交主要在1.44%-1.46%；上日在1.45%-1.46%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與銀行承做兩周內拆款利率成交區間在1.38%-1.40%，同上日</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述交易員不願具名接受採訪，因未被授權公開評論</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣短票市場：30天自保票上交易日平均利率1.455%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣債券發行預覽：聯上開發；台電；東元；元大證券；政府公債</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣貨幣市場資金預覽：央行存單到期1.3兆元；財政部舉新還舊</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場動態</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博追蹤櫃買中心數據，10年熱券電子盤無成交</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5年熱券電子盤無成交</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台股加權指數上漲0.9%，報30567.29點</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據彭博數據，5年期利率交換報2.045%，基本持平</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國10年期國債殖利率紐約尾盤報4.1653%，亞洲盤因日本休市而未開盤</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台北時間14:00，據拆款中心數據，隔夜拆款加權平均利率在0.808%， 區間在0.805%-0.825%，上日收在0.815%</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2-7天平均利率在1.186%， 區間在0.96%-1.41%</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上交易日當日超額準備為546億元台幣；本提存期累計超額準備為6038億元台幣，加計前期1%超額準備為1兆151億元台幣</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至上交易日，央行定存單未到期餘額為7兆4479.7億元台幣，上日減發384.2億元</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">重點關注</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台灣對美國全年貿易順差創新高 或使關稅談判更加複雜</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美債交易員仍青睞殖利率曲線陡峭策略 關注焦點轉向本周美國通膨數據</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗抗議浪潮愈演愈烈 一場可能改寫全球格局的革命悄然逼近</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛預計美國2026年經濟成長強勁且通膨溫和 聯儲會將降息兩次</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著「嬰兒潮」一代向Z世代交棒 美國債券需求或將趨緩</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-%E5%85%AC%E5%82%B5%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%86%B7%E6%B8%85-irs%E6%A9%AB%E5%90%91%E7%9B%A4%E6%95%B4-%E7%9F%AD%E7%A5%A8%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E7%95%A5%E8%B5%B0%E8%BB%9F-060638183.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-12 14:50:53",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "伊朗稱已平息抗議活動 並指控以色列和美國幕後煽動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 伊朗外長表示，在持續兩周的動盪後，安全部隊已「完全掌控」國家局勢，並指責以色列和美國煽動全國性抗議活動，導致數百人喪生。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗外長阿拉格齊重申伊朗政府的指控，稱「暴亂分子和恐怖分子」使用「達伊沙式暴力」殺害警察和平民、破壞公共財產。此處「達伊沙」系伊斯蘭國的阿拉伯語縮寫。抗議活動持續至周一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿拉格齊在接受國家電視台採訪時稱，「我們掌握大量證據，證明美國和以色列干涉了這場恐怖主義戰爭」，並補充道，「以色列直接負有責任，而美國通過煽動暴力的言論也難辭其咎。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-29899908-61db-3f66-9814-b6f90fe7c7e0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：[深度] 伊朗抗議浪潮愈演愈烈 一場可能改寫全球格局的革命悄然逼近</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Iran Says It’s Quelled Protests After Hundreds Reported Killed</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%B2%E5%B9%B3%E6%81%AF%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E4%B8%A6%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E5%92%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95-104535450.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-12 19:36:06",
