            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普稱如果信用卡公司不限制利率就違法了",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普表示，如果信用卡發卡機構不聽從他的呼籲，把利率上限設在10%一年時間，那麼它們就「違反了法律」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普周日從佛羅里達州返回華盛頓時在空軍一號上對記者講話，再次重申了他此前的要求，即信用卡發行機構必須將利率降至10%，並維持一年不變。他設定了1月20日的最後期限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普說，如果到那時還沒有限制利率，「那它們就是違法的。有些機構收取28%，接近30%的利率。人們不知道自己要支付30%的利率。他們辛勤工作，卻完全不知道自己要支付30%的利率。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7bc73ca5-5dfa-34e0-a644-2c5ae1b975f7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他談到大型銀行時說道：「它們真的濫用了信用卡。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普要求限制利率的提議並沒有立法支持，他也沒有解釋貸款機構如何違反法律。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此，這些評論還是使得摩根大通、Capital One Financial Corp.和花旗集團等機構成為關注焦點。巴克萊股價倫敦時間08:20下跌4.2%，該公司在美國擁有信用卡業務。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Says Credit Card Firms Violate Law If Rates Not Capped (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Paige Smith.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B8%8D%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E5%B0%B1%E9%81%95%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%86-090100441.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-12 18:15:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "共和黨要員抨擊司法部調查 川普「馴服」聯儲會計畫遇阻力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Aaron Schwartz/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oeewblcb8xKvAau4Mwbz4Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/93760868047ae4d64dcd4399f6c5c04b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Aaron Schwartz/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>主席<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:鮑威爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鮑威爾\">鮑威爾</a>指責美國司法部以啟動大陪審團調查為借口對該央行施壓並恐嚇後，總統川普周日晚間即遭到部分兩黨議員抨擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:參議院銀行委員會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/參議院銀行委員會\">參議院銀行委員會</a>中的關鍵共和黨人Thom Tillis誓言在該問題解決之前，將反對川普提名的任何聯儲會候選人。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Aaron Schwartz/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PbTZmOqjhZPW0QxENjrRjA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8e98586f31e9766e077df5db0960211b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Aaron Schwartz/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「如果之前還有人懷疑川普政府內的顧問是否真的在力圖終結聯儲會的獨立性，那麼現在應該沒有絲毫疑問了，」 Tillis在一份聲明中稱。「如今受到質疑的是司法部的獨立性和公信力。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a3710518-b5fa-39f8-adcc-296cdcc5cb7f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在這一法律問題得到徹底解決前，我將反對確認任何聯儲會提名人選——包括即將出現的聯儲會主席空缺，」 Tillis表示。他同時也是參議院司法委員會的成員。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普數月來一直明確表示，他希望聯儲會迅速大幅降息。多個政府部門將矛頭對准了麗莎·庫克等聯儲會理事，現在又輪到鮑威爾。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鮑威爾在周日晚間發布的書面和視頻聲明中稱，司法部此舉與他去年6月在國會就聯儲會總部翻修工程所作的證詞有關。但他表示，這「應當放在本屆政府威脅和持續施壓聯儲會這一背景下看待」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">鮑威爾補充道，「這關乎聯儲會能否繼續基於實證和經濟狀況來設定利率，還是貨幣政策將受到政治壓力或恐嚇左右。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周日接受NBC News採訪時，川普否認知曉司法部對聯儲會調查一事。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：鮑威爾稱司法部已向聯儲會發出傳票 威脅提起刑事訴訟</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Tillis的威脅可能會阻礙川普想要讓聯儲會聽從其意志行事的計畫。他的反對很可能導致任何聯儲會提名人選在參議院銀行委員會陷入僵局，該委員會的兩黨成員組成目前為13-11。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">民主黨人則迅速發表聲明予以譴責。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「川普想要提名一位新的聯儲會主席，並徹底將鮑威爾趕出理事會，以完成他對央行的腐敗接管，」參議院銀行委員會的民主黨人伊麗莎白·沃倫寫道。「他像個妄圖成為獨裁者的人一樣濫用法律，以求讓聯儲會為他和他的億萬富翁朋友們服務。參議院絕不能推進任何川普提名的聯儲會人選。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">參議院民主黨領袖查克·舒默表示，破壞聯儲會的獨立性將危及經濟。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「任何獨立思考、不盲從川普的人都會受到調查，」他指出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Faces Fed Roadblock as Key Republican Blasts Justice Probe</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
